    <item>
      <title>Re: Version support</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/xrowmetadata/forum/general/version_support/re_version_support</link>
      <description>Hi Brendan,&#13;
&#13;
The reason is that you don't have fresh content on your site (30 days).&#13;
&#13;
The extension creates 2 sitemaps: One with "fresh content" and one with "old" content.&#13;
&#13;
There are 2 cronjobs for that.&#13;
&#13;
So my tip is:&#13;
Add this in your settings/override/cronjob.ini.append.php:&#13;
&#13;
[CronjobPart-sitemap]&#13;
Scripts[]&#13;
Scripts[]=archivesitemap.php&#13;
Scripts[]=sitemap.php&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
php runcronjobs.php sitemap &#13;
calls both scripts.</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Georg Franz)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/xrowmetadata/forum/general/version_support/re_version_support</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Jun 2012 17:06:28 +0000</pubDate>
    </item>
